• Setting a custom OpenGL version may <b><font color="@colorError">cause game crashes or rendering issues — proceed with caution</font></b>!<br/>
• If any issues occur, please <b><font color="@colorError">disable this feature</font></b> first!<br/>
• Once you enable this feature, we will <b><font color="@colorError">no longer accept</font></b> any bug reports related to additional issues! Before reporting problems, please make sure to <b><font color="@colorError">disable this feature</font></b>!<br/>
