<string name="menu_item_remove">Remove VinzzRender related files</string>  
<string name="remove_mg_files_message"><![CDATA[This action will completely delete all files associated with VinzzRender. This includes:<br/><br/>

• <b>All configuration files:</b> Any of your custom settings, preferences, and possible configuration files required for the application to run will be removed.<br/>
• <b>Cache files:</b> The GLSL cache generated by VinzzRender during runtime (used to speed up loading) will be cleared.<br/>
• <b>Log files:</b> Log files generated during the operation of VinzzRender will be deleted.<br/><br/>
Please note, this action is <b><font color="@colorError">irreversible</font></b>. Once you click "OK", all the files mentioned above will be permanently deleted and cannot be recovered. If you are going to use VinzzRender again in the future, you will need to reconfigure it.<br/><br/>
<b><font color="@colorError">Are you sure you want to continue?</font></b>]]></string>
